title: Destiny.PS3.B0XUP FIXED FILES + TUTORIAL
description:
This contains Destiny.PS3.UNLIMITED (Thanks to our friends from UNLIMITED for leaking the game!)

And it has the fixed files (no black screen)

And it has the 1.02 Update PKG.

READREADREADREADREADREADREADREAD

For this to work on DEX:
Go to Debug Settings
Change Boot Mode to "Release Mode"

For this to work anyway:
Go on Multiman.
Press Square on the game.
Enable BD Mirror.
Click Start.
It will say some stuff about firmware, just click YES.
Now the eboot of the game should be patched to 4.50/below and will work on any firmware. ( Original Eboot requires 4.65 spoofer/firmware )
